n千祈唔好單獨人小既情況同警察硬碰<br />\n唔係要打警察係要避警察 要消耗警力 <br />\n被人驅散左 要再上翻去馬路人<br />\n儘量以遊擊消耗警方力量<br />\n要有共識<br />\n<br />\n唔好係佢安排好既區域發聲<br />\n要係影響到香港經濟既地方發聲<br />\n最好係銀行街同港交所街道<br />\n主要佔領到 核心交通道路就已經有談判籌碼<br />\n爭取足夠大既國際目光注意支持<br />\n<br />\n佔領完一定要留守！<br />\n除非政府武力清場<br />\n就先去其他據點<br />\n之後再佔領<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n後勤支援既送糧食 水等物資<br />\n時刻留意 群組睇佔領情況 更新所需物資再作支援<br />\n<br />\n1.車 單車(堵塞交通 建立領地 ）<br />\n2.貨物(堵塞交通 建立領地) <br />\n膠帆布 等等佔領視野體積大既貨品<br />\n3.大聲公 鼓/龍洲鼓 對講機<br />\n（引導其他未有共識既人群 提升士氣） <br />\n4.保護自己既裝備同武器<br />\n以保護自己做更長時間抗爭為主<br />\n唔建議著校服<br />\n(唔係用於攻擊而係保護好自己）<br />\n<br />\n大家仲有見到不足歡迎補充<br />\n<br />\n撤銷引導條例 <br />\n還我獨立司法香港🇭🇰"},{"pid":"78194a8378d01c181095fe8055936d1e64a7d1fb","tid":1199231,"uid":143708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:41:46.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"65616461e1f6091c70e5cd44df49cbf6587cec98","tid":1199231,"uid":4701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T14:48:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e43bd4fbbbd07e4bb4e499ec2f7512d0a79e7bd8","tid":1199231,"uid":4701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:00:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6033fe9c3ef15ccd37cbffa5b78d91d66b00ccb2","tid":1199231,"uid":4701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T15:33:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f59d1a93ec1603f342f6345f629c7c95c926fc7f","tid":1199231,"uid":4701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl